&lt;li&gt;Partner with local operating teams to understand business activity, improve data accuracy, and support informed decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with annual audits and maintain organized supporting documentation for financial and compliance requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
